Schedule of Events
</h2>

<h3>
Friday, August 24
</h3>

<p>
<strong>7:00 pm Weekend Kickoff Party</strong>
<br />Mt. Washington Hotel South Veranda
</p>

<h3>
Saturday, August 25
</h3>

<p>
<strong>7:00 - 10:00 am Breakfast Buffet</strong>
